<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=0">
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
		<title>绝世武神微信签到活动</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/css/index.css" />
		<script  type="text/javascript" src="http://s.gyyx.cn/Lib/jquery.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/js/gyyx_wxshare.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/js/index.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		
		<div  class="checkin_main">
			<input type="hidden" id="openId" name="openId" value="$openId"/>
			<img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/checkInTopImg.png"/>
			
			<div class="checkin_con">
				<p class="checkin_num">当前您的积分为：<span>$userScore</span></p>
				<ul class="checkin_btn clear">
					<li><a href="javascript:;" class="js_dhLog"><img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/qdBtn1.png" alt="" /></a></li>
					<li><a href="javascript:;" class="js_qdBtn"><img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/qdBtn2.png" alt="" /></a></li>
					<li><a href="/jswswxsign/toIntegralMall?openId=$openId"><img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/qdBtn3.png" alt="" /></a></li>
				</ul>
				
				<div class="checkin_rule">
					<p class="rule_tit">活动规则</p>
					<ul>
						<li class="clear">
							<b>•</b>
							<p>关注绝世武神手游资讯站（<span class="yellow">jswssyzxz</span>）公众号方可参加签到有礼活动。</p>
						</li>
						
						<li class="clear">
							<b>•</b>
							<p>
								每天签到即可获得10积分<br />
								连续签到<span class="yellow">5天</span>可额外获得<span class="yellow">20积分</span><br />
								连续签到<span class="yellow">10天</span>可额外获得<span class="yellow">40积分</span><br />
								连续签到<span class="yellow">20天</span>可额外获得<span class="yellow">60积分</span><br />
								连续签到<span class="yellow">30天</span>可额外获得<span class="yellow">100积分</span>，积累到达指定积分即可兑换相应游戏礼包。
							</p>
						</li>
						
						<li class="clear">
							<b>•</b>
							<p>活动期间，单个微信账号每日仅能签到一次。</p>
						</li>
						
						<li class="clear">
							<b>•</b>
							<p>积分商城的游戏礼包将以兑换码的形式发放，请到游戏内兑换使用。</p>
						</li>

					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="alert_box">
			<div class="alert_con">
				<img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/alert_qdBg.png"/>
				<div class="con_text">
					
					<div class="qd_yq" style="display: none;">
						<p>亲爱的玩家~</p>
						<p class="yq_info"></p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="qd_succ" style="display: none;">
						<p class="qd_tit">亲爱的玩家~您已完成今日签到！</p>
						<p class="qd_day">目前您已连续签到<span></span>天！<br />
							恭喜获取<b></b>积分
						</p>
						<p>请继续努力吧！</p>
						<p class="dh_tip">（游戏礼包请点击积分商城进行兑换）</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="qd_dhLog" style="display: none;">
						<p>亲爱的玩家~您当前已兑换的礼包：</p>
						<ul></ul>
						<p class="dh_tip">（请到游戏内进行兑换吧！）</p>
					</div>
					
					<a href="javascript:;" class="js_close"><img src="http://static.cn114.cn/action/jswswxsign/images/qdBg.png"/></a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="dia_modal_nouse js_nouse" style="display:none;">请在竖屏查看！</div>
	</body>
</html>
  
    

    